      "content": "```python\ndef solve_vrp(distance_matrix):\n    n = len(distance_matrix)\n    visited = [False] * n\n    route = [0]\n    total_distance = 0\n\n    current_node = 0\n    visited[current_node] = True\n\n    while len(route) < n:\n        next_node = None\n        min_distance = float('inf')\n\n        for i in range(n):\n            if not visited[i] and distance_matrix[current_node][i] < min_distance:\n                min_distance = distance_matrix[current_node][i]\n                next_node = i\n\n        route.append(next_node)\n        visited[next_node] = True\n        total_distance += min_distance\n        current_node = next_node\n\n    # Return to starting node\n    total_distance += distance_matrix[current_node][0]\n    route.append(0)\n\n    return total_distance\n\n# Test cases for my current dataset\nmatrix1 = [\n    [0, 10, 15, 20],\n    [10, 0, 35, 25],\n    [15, 35, 0, 30],\n    [20, 25, 30, 0]\n]\nassert solve_vrp(matrix1) == 80",
